%% entity A: Opens a local Mermaid source file for viewing.
%% entity B: Checks whether the diagram can continue through the render flow.
%% relation Yes: The input is valid and processing may continue.
%% relation No: The input is invalid and the viewer reports the problem.
flowchart LR
    A[Open .mmd file] --> B{Valid Mermaid?}
    B -- Yes --> C[Render diagram]
    C --> D[Zoom and pan]
    B -- No --> E[Show helpful error]
